Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.15,0:00:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This spring, Atlus brings you
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.68,0:00:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a slightly naughty jigsaw game recommended for ages 18 and above.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.17,0:00:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"My Best Friends: St. Andrew Girls' School", Sega Saturn edition.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.80,0:00:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In "My Best Friends" you can assemble \Na 7 x 10-piece jigsaw puzzle.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.66,0:00:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on how fast you complete it, you'll be able to watch some erotic animations.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.57,0:00:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's explain the game in practice.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.44,0:01:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you choose one out of five girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the self-introduction begins.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.00,0:01:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Ayano.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I am 17 years old, Gemini.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.82,0:01:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the head of the photography club.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.04,0:01:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And today I'm supposed to be a model myself,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.50,0:01:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not sure what kind of poses to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.37,0:01:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Take off my glasses?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.03,0:01:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.99,0:01:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the stills during her introduction
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.70,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes the base for the puzzle.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.90,0:01:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where the puzzle starts.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.47,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the C button to pick up the piece \Nor to place it if you've found where it fits.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.16,0:01:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you pick up a piece that you don't know where to place, you can discard it with the B button.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.95,0:01:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you own a Sega Saturn Shuttle Mouse™️, \Nplaying becomes even more comfortable.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.24,0:02:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Isn't it easy?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.42,0:02:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's finished, you'll see another anime scene.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.65,0:02:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The less time it took you to assemble the puzzle, the more perverted it becomes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.02,0:02:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a total of eight girls in this game.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.89,0:02:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It uses 2750 animation cells for smooth movement. {probably means animation cells? lol so maybe like 2750 frames total?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you pick "Girls' introduction" in the mode selector,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be able to view the full profile of that character.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.89,0:02:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, you'll only be able to choose from five girls, so pay attention. {?? idk to what}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.60,0:02:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the other three...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.14,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get a chance to enjoy your time with them once you've beaten the main game. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.08,0:03:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was a puzzle game for Sega Saturn—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.27,0:03:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"My Best Friends: St. Andrew Girls' School."
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.75,0:03:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it starting on March 22nd for a recommended price of 6,800 yen, from Atlus!
